
NOTE: you must have a valid Sauce Labs user account.

steps:

run these commands:

npm i -g saucectl

# or the same command above using curl: curl -L https://saucelabs.github.io/saucectl/install | bash

saucectl new (pick puppeteer)

export SAUCE_USERNAME=<your-username>
export SAUCE_ACCESS_KEY=<your-access-key>

saucectl new
This command will ask you to choose a framework between Puppeteer and Playwright.
Choose Puppeteer

saucectl run

NOTE: to adjust what tests are executed look in this file ./sauce/config.yml 
